-- To check the current value of JOB_QUEUE_PROCESSES\nSHOW PARAMETER job_queue_processes;\n\n-- To alter the value of JOB_QUEUE_PROCESSES to 0 (This must be done by a user with appropriate privileges)\nALTER SYSTEM SET job_queue_processes=0 SCOPE=BOTH SID='*';\n\n-- Note: Altered parameter values might require a restart or can take effect immediately depending on the scope (MEMORY, SPFILE, BOTH).